==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unsparing
<hw>Un*spar"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>un-</ets> not + <ets>sparing</ets>, p. pr. of
<ets>spare</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Not sparing; not parsimonious; liberal;
profuse.</def> <rj><au>Burke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not merciful or forgiving.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un*spar"ing*ly</wf> <pr>(#)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos>
-- <wf>Un*spar"ing*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unspeak</ent>⟦br⟧
